\c 19
\p
\v 1 Zvino kwakaudzwa Joabhu, tarira, mambo anochema nekuungudzira Abhusaromu.
\v 2 Zvino ruponeso rwezuva iro kwakava kuchema kuvanhu vese, nokuti vanhu vakanzwa zuva iro zvichinzi: Mambo anochema mwanakomana wake.
\v 3 Zvino vanhu vakapinda vachiverevedza muguta nezuva iro sevanhu vanoverevedza vane nyadzi vachitiza kuhondo.
\v 4 Asi Mambo wakafukidza chiso chake, mambo ndokuchema nenzwi guru, achiti: Mwanakomana wangu Abhusaromu, Abhusaromu, mwanakomana wangu, mwanakomana wangu!
\v 5 Zvino Joabhu wakapinda mumba kuna mambo, ndokuti: Wanyadzisa nhasi manyadza zviso zvevaranda venyu vese vaponesa upenyu hwenyu nhasi, neupenyu hwevanakomana nevanasikana venyu, neupenyu hwevakadzi venyu, neupenyu hwevarongo venyu.
\v 6 Pakuda vavengi venyu nekuvenga vanokudai. Nokuti wazivisa nhasi kuti hauna machinda nevaranda havasi chinhu kwauri, nokuti ndaziva nhasi kuti dai Abhusaromu aiva ari mupenyu, uye isu tese takafa nhasi, kuti zvingadai zvakanaka pameso ako.
\v 7 Naizvozvo ikozvino, buda unotaura kumoyo yevaranda vako; nokuti ndinopika naJehovha, kana ukasabuda, zvirokwazvo hakuna munhu achagara newe usiku huno. Zvino izvi zvichava zvakaipa kupfuura zvakaipa zvese zvakakuwira kubva paudiki hwako kusvika nhasi.
\v 8 Zvino mambo wakasimuka ndokugara pasuwo. Zvino vakaudza vanhu vese, vachiti: Tarirai, mambo agere pasuwo; vanhu vese ndokuuya pamberi pamambo. Zvino Israeri wese waiva atiza umwe neumwe kuenda kutende rake.
\s Dhavhidhi anodzokera Jerusarema
\p
\v 9 AZvino zvakaitika kuti vanhu vese vaiva vachipikisana kumarudzi ese Israeri, vachiti: Mambo wakatiponesa paruoko rwevavengi vedu, akatinunura paruoko rwevaFirisitia, zvino ikozvino watiza panyika nokuda kwaAbhusaromu.
\v 10 Asi Abhusaromu watakazodza pamusoro pedu wafira muhondo. Zvino ikozvino munonyararirei \add pa\add*kudzosa mambo?
\p
\v 11 Zvino mambo Dhavhidhi wakatuma \add nhume\add* kuna Zhadhoki nekuna Abhiatari vapristi achiti: Taurai kuvakuru vaJudha, muti: Imi munononokereiko kudzosa mambo kumba kwake? Nokuti mambo wakanzwa kuti VaIsraeri vese vanotaura kuti adzoswe kumba kwake.
\v 12 Muri hama dzangu, muri fupa rangu nenyama yangu, naizvozvo sei muri vekupedzisira kudzosa mambo?
\v 13 Zvino muti kuna Amasa: Iwe hausi pfupa rangu nenyama yangu here? Mwari ngaaite saizvozvo kwandiri, ngaawedzere saizvozvo, kana iwe usingazovi mukuru wehondo pamberi pangu mazuva ese pachinzvimbo chaJoabhu.
\v 14 Zvino wakadzoredzera moyo yevanhu vese vaJudha semunhu umwe; ivo ndokutuma \add nhume\add* kuna mambo \add vachiti\add*: Dzokai, imwi nevaranda venyu vese.
\v 15 Mambo ndokudzoka ndokusvika paJoridhani, Judha ndokusvika paGirigari, kuenda kunosangana namambo, kuyambusa mambo Joridhani.
\p
\v 16 Zvino Shimei mwanakomana waGera, muBhenjamini, waiva weBhahurimu, wakakurumidza ndokuburuka nevarume vaJudha kuchingamidza mambo Dhavhidhi.
\v 17 Nechuru chevanhu vekwaBhenjamini vaiva naye, naZibha muranda weimba yaSauro, nevanakomana vake gumi nevashanu, nevaranda vake makumi maviri vanaye; ndokukurumidza kuyambukira kuJoridhani pamberi pamambo.
\v 18 Zvino kwakayambuka igwa kunoyambusa imba yamambo, nekuita izvo zvakanaka pameso ake. Zvino Shimei mwanakomana waGera wakawira pasi pamberi papamambo pakuyambuka kwake Joridhani.
\v 19 Ndokuti kuna mambo: Ishe wangu ngaarege kuverengera kuipa kwandiri, kana kurangarira izvo muranda wenyu zvaakaita pakutsauka zuva mambo raakabuda muJerusarema, ktu mambo azviise mumoyo make.
\v 20 Nokuti muranda wenyu anoziva kuti ndakatadza; zvino tarirai, ndasvika nhasi ndiri wekutanga weimba yaJosefa kuburuka kuzochingamidza ishe wangu mambo.
\v 21 Asi Abhishai mwanakomana waZeruya wakapindura ndokuti: Shimei haangaurawi here nekuda kweichi, nokuti wakatuka muzodzwa waJehovha?
\v 22 Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Ndinei nemwi, kuti nhasi muve vadzivisi vanguimwi vanakomana vaZeruya, kuti muve vadzivisi kwandiri nhasi. Kuchaurawa munhu kwaIsraeri nhasi here? Nekuti handizivi here kuti nhasi ndiri mambo pamusoro paIsraeri?
\v 23 Mambo ndokuti kuna Shimei: Haungafi. Mambo ndokupika kwaari.
\p
\v 24 Zvino Mefibhosheti mwanakomana waSauro wakaburuka kuchingamidza mambo; asi waiva asina kugadzirira tsoka dzake, kana kugadzirira ndebvu dzake, kana kusuka nguvo dzake, kubva pazuva mambo raakaenda kusvika zuva raakadzoka naro nerugare.
\v 25 Zvino zvakaitika paakasvika kuJerusarema kuchingamidza mambo, kuti mambo wakati kwaari: Wakaregerei kuenda neni, Mefibhosheti?
\v 26 Iye ndokuti: Ishe wangu, mambo, muranda wangu wakandinyengera; nokuti muranda wenyu wakati: Ndichazviisira chigaro pambongoro kuti ndiitasve, ndigoenda namambo, nokuti muranda wenyu wakaremara.
\v 27 Uye akanochera muranda wenyu kuna ishe wangu, mambo; asi ishe wangu mambo wakaita semutumwa waMwari, naizvozvo itai zvakanaka pameso enyu.
\v 28 Nokuti imba yese yababa vangu dai isiri chinhu kunze kwekuva varume verufu pamberi pashe wangu mambo; kunyange zvakadaro makaisa muranda wenyu pakati pevaidya patafura yenyu. Zvino ndichine kodzeroi kuti ndichemezve kuna mambo?
\v 29 Mambo ndokuti kwaari: Ucharamba uchitaurei nyaya dzako? Ndinoti: Iwe naZibha govanai nyika.
\v 30 Mefibhosheti ndokuti kuna mambo: Haiwa ngaatore zvese, ishe wangu mambo zvaakadzokera kumba kwake nerugare.
\p
\v 31 NaBharizirai muGiriyadhi waiva aburuka kubva kuRogerimi ndokuyambuka Joridhani namambo, kumuperekedza mhiri kwaJoridhani.
\v 32 Zvino Bharizirai waiva mutana kwazvo, uye waiva atsigira mambo pazvekudya zvavo paMahanaimi, nokuti waiva munhu mukuru kwazvo.
\v 33 Mambo ndokuti kuna Bharizirai: Hendei, tiyambuke tese, ini ndichakuraramisa kwandiri paJerusarema.
\v 34 Bharizirai akati kuna mambo: Makore oupenyu hwangu achava manganiko, kuti ndikwire Jerusarema namambo?
\v 35 Nhasi ndava wemakore makumi masere; ini ndichagona kutsaura zvakanaka kune zvakaipa here? Muranda wenyu uchagona kuravira zvakanaka zvaanodya kana zvaanonwa here? Ndichagona kunzwa manzwi avarume navakadzi kana vachiimba here? Muranda wenyu ucharemedzereiko ishe wangu mambo?
\v 36 Muranda wenyu wakange achingoda hake kuyambuka Joridhani namambo; zvino mambo ungandiripira izvozvo nomubairo wakadai seiko?
\v 37 Regai, muranda wenyu adzoke hake, ndinofira hangu muguta rangu, pamarinda ababa vangu namai vangu; asi hoyo muranda wenyu Chimhamu, iye ngaayambuke nashe wangu mambo, mugomuitira iye sezvamunoda.
\v 38 Mambo akapindura akati: Chimhamu uchayambuka neni, ini ndichamuitira iye sezvaunoda iwe; zvese zvaunoreva kwandiri ndichakuitira izvo.
\v 39 Vanhu vese vakayambuka Joridhani, naiye mambo akayambukawo; mambo akatsvoda Bharizirai akamuropafadza, iye akadzokera kumusha kwake.
\v 40 Naizvozvo mambo akapfuurira Girigari, Chimhamu akayambuka naye, navanhu vese vaJudha vakapfuudzira mberi mambo, uyewo hafu yavanhu VaIsraeri.
\p
\v 41 Zvino varume vese VaIsraeri vakauya kuna mambo, vakati kuna mambo: Hama dzedu, varume vaJudha, vakakubireiko, vakayambusa mambo naveimba yake Joridhani, pamwe chete navarume vese vaDhavhidhi?
\v 42 Varume vese vaJudha vakapindura varume VaIsraeri, vakati: Nokuti mambo ihama yedu yomumba; matsamwireiko nemhaka iyi? Ko isu takatongodya zvamambo here? Iye wakatongotipa chipo here?
\v 43 Varume VaIsraeri vakapindura varume vaJudha, vakati: Isu tine migove ine gumi kuna mambo, naDhavhidhi ndewedu kukunda imi; zvino imwi makatizvidzireiko, zvamusina kutanga kurangana nesu pamusoro pokudzosa mambo wedu? Asi mashoko avarume vaJudha akange achityisa kukunda mashoko avarume VaIsraeri.
